{
  "stem": "15393.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Blond, tall, blue-eyed, mane of blond hair, absolutely one can say gorgeous to look at if it weren't for this horrid uniform on top.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I used to take this with me as my document, because I thought, well, so long as I seem all right, nothing, I'm fine.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when I feel-- and feeling went a long way in those days, you know, and instinct.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You had a sixth sense, no doubt, about that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You knew when somebody was looking at you from the back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And sort of, you felt it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When I feel a little bit uncomfortable, I unfold this thing, very visibly, ostentatiously almost.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And take out some money from there or whatever from there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when anybody sees this, that's that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was my document.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm only sorry I haven't kept it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I haven't got any sign, any-- any trace of this, because that was truly, on many occasions, my document.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And on a number of occasions, I would come to shop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I never went into the queue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I must say, with the-- the pure Germanic attitude that they had, you know, their-- their chutzpah, if I might call it that, I would go immediately to the top and demand to be served, which was a terrible thing to do.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I said, I have no time to wait here in queues and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the people, who were waiting, were not German, so they were underdogs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They could wait, in other words.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I am not the one to wait.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I haven't got the time to wait.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Please, this and this and this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This is what I need.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And off I went, because I was afraid to stand there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I would produce my thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
